2020-11-14T07:16:48Z	🎉 **NEW:** With the merge of [PR 269](https://github.com/jointwt/twtxt/pull/269) which closes [Issue 264](https://github.com/jointwt/twtxt/issues/264), we will no longer store email address at all! But how will you recover your password in case you forget it you say?! 😳 Easy! You just enter the same email address you used when you signed up on the password reset page. If it matches a one-way cryptographic hash of the email you originally used, we'll send a password reset token to that email address, if not whoops!
